# Project Structure Conventions

## `app/lib/` — generic, reusable utilities only

Only place **framework-agnostic, project-unaware** utilities here. These should be portable to any project.

✅ OK: `use-keyboard-shortcut.ts`, `use-is-mobile.ts`, `utils.ts`  
❌ NOT OK: anything that imports app routes, store, or domain types

## `app/components/` — everything app-specific

All hooks and logic that reference app routes, stores, or domain concepts belong here, even if they have no JSX.

✅ OK: `use-navigate-shortcuts.ts`, `use-labels-shortcut.ts`
